page.title: 20Transport,Sherburn-in-Elmet
page.content:
Tadcaster road, the route to York and the coast, is busiest.Leeds road has least traffic.Selby road has most agricultural traffic.At the end of New Lane it is busy between 8.45 and 9.00 also 3.45 to 4.00.This is because the High School pupils are bused to and from school from a wide area.
